@node History "Historie vydįnķ DT2NI"
@prev Future
@next Main

@{b}@{FG fill}Ponechįno v originįle.@{FG text}@{ub}

@{u}1.0@{uu}

First Release


@{u}1.1@{uu}

Bug fixed - @{b}DT2NI@{ub} worked only with picture.datatype for CGX (Thanks to @{b}Terry Fry@{ub})


@{u}1.2@{uu}

New features: process single file, give a default tool, create greyscaled icons, save tooltypes with information about picture

New arguments: DEFTOOL/K,GREY/K/N,NOTOOLTYPES/S

Now includes swedish catalog (Thanks to @{b}TorbjÉrn Aronsson@{ub})

Now works on 68000 (I think it should have worked on 68000 all the time)


@{u}1.3@{uu}

Bug fixed - if the SIZE/N got a too big number no error was printed.

Now @{b}DT2NI@{ub} does not replace existing normal icon images. If the argument NOTOOLTYPES is given existing tooltypes will be copied.

A second (inverted) image can be created to show the selected icon. Option: SECONDIMAGE/S

French catalog added (Thanks to @{b}Jerome Chesnot@{ub})

Norwegian catalog added (Thanks to @{b}Kim Roar Utsi@{ub})

Spanish catalog added (Thanks to @{b}Leopoldo Gomez@{ub})

Greek catalog added (Thanks to @{b}Elias Papanikolaou@{ub})


@{u}1.4@{uu}

Now HAM and EHB pictures are supported.

New feature: you can use the standard NewIcons palette (16 colors). Option: NICONCOLORS/S.

New feature: if you wish the black border that makes the icons square is not created. Option: NOBACKFILL/S.

I changed the code that maps the truecolor image down. Now it is a slower but more variable.

The chapter "Bugs" has changed to "Bugs and problems".

The beginning sentence in chapter "Future has changed" :)

The chapter "How does it work?" has been deleted.

Spanish guide added (Thanks to @{b}Leopoldo Gomez@{ub})

Now there is a support page:
  http://home.t-online.de/home/060334252-0001/

@endnode


@node Bugs "Chybiēky a problémy"
@prev Thanks
@next Future

@{u}Chyby@{uu}

Dosud nebyly zaznamenįny łįdné chyby.

Pokud byste nėjaké chyby naīel, poīlete @{" mi " link Author} prosķm zprįvu.


@{u}Problémy@{uu}

Zdį se, łe picture.datatype verze 43 mį problémy s obrįzky ve formįtu HAM. Tyto obrįzky jsou nahrįvįny v 64 nebo 256 barvįch.

Nėkdy se zhroutķ systém bėhem tvorby velmi velkżch ikon ve 256 barvįch a nastavenżm argumentem "SECONDIMAGE". Osobnė si myslķm, łe to nenķ problém programu @{b}DT2NI@{ub}, ale łe potķłe zapźķēińuje newicon.library nebo Workbench.

@endnode


@node Future "Co se chystį v dalīķch verzķch"
@prev Bugs
@next History

V dalīķch verzķch programu @{b}DT2NI@{ub} chystįm tato vylepīenķ:

- GUI (opravdu bude!)

- Optimalizace barev

- Jinż pomėr stran neł jen 1:1

- Dithering

- Nebude dochįzet k pźepsįnķ jił existujķcķch ikon

- Vķce katalogū

- Chcete nėco dalīķho? Poīlete @{" mi " link "Author"} tedy vaīe nįvrhy.

@endnode

@node Requirements "Co potźebujete ke spuītėnķ DT2NI?"
@prev Introduction
@next Usage

@{b}DT2NI@{ub} pro sprįvné fungovįnķ vyładuje:

  OS 3.0 nebo vyīīķ
  @{" newicon.library " link "Thanks"}

  Datatypy pro pźķsluīné obrįzkové formįty

@{u}Doporuēuji:@{uu}

  picture.datatype V43 pro obrįzky s vėtīķ neł 8bitovou hloubkou
  Workbench s paletou true- nebo high-color

@{b}DT2NI@{ub} byl testovįn a vyvķjen na této konfiguraci:

  Amiga 4000T, 68040/25MHz, CyberVision64

  OS 3.1
  newicon.library 39.1
  datatypes.library 45.3

  picture.datatype 43.759 (CyberGraphX)
  picture.datatype 43.24 (Picasso 96)
  picture.datatype 40.4

  CyberGraphX V3

Mįm zprįvy od ułivatelū, łe @{b}DT2NI@{ub} funguje s:

  OS 3.0
  CyberStorm 060
  EGSSpectrum + Picasso 96
  CyberVision64 + CyberGraphX V2
  Blizzard 1230-IV

@endnode


@node Introduction "Pįr slov śvodem"
@prev Copyright
@next Requirements

@{b}DT2NI@{ub} je program spouītėnż z shellu, kterż vytvįźķ ze vīech obrįzkū, které je schopen nahrįt pomocķ @{" datatypes.library " link "Requirements"} ikony formįtu @{" NewIcons " link "Requirements"}.

Kromė toho vįm umołnķ definovat nėkteré @{" volby " link "Usage"}, napź. velikost ikon.

Vytvįźķ ikony ał ve 256 barvįch.

@{b}DT2NI@{ub} podporuje pochopitelnė i locale.library.

@endnode


@node Usage "Jak se to vlastnė poułķvį"
@prev Requirements
@next Author

@{b}DT2NI@{ub} podporuje nįsledujķcķ argumenty:

@{u}DIR/A@{uu}
Adresįź nebo soubor, kde bude hledįn obrįzek. Toto je NUTNŻ argument!

@{u}SIZE/N@{uu}
Rozmėry ikony. Tato hodnota musķ bżt v rozmezķ od 25 do 92 pixelū. Standardnė je nastaveno 40 pixelū.

@{u}ALL/S@{uu}
Ikony se vytvoźķ podle vīech obrįzkū v adresįźi.

@{u}QUIET/S@{uu}
Potlaēķ témėź vīechen vżstup.

@{u}FAST/S@{uu}
Poułije se rychlejīķ algoritmus mėźenķ (vżslednį ikona je mķrnė horīķ kvality).

@{u}NOSORT/S@{uu}
Obsah adresįźe se pźi naēķtįnķ netźķdķ (prohledįvįnķ je o nėco rychlejīķ).

@{u}DEFTOOL/K@{uu}
Nįzev pźiźazeného programu (standardnė se pźiźadķ "MultiView").

@{u}GREY/K/N@{uu}
Vytvoźķ se ikony ve stupnķch īedi. Mūłete zadat jednu z nįsledujķcķch hodnot: 4, 8, 16, 32, 64, 128 nebo 256. Jakįkoli jinį hodnota zapźķēinķ, łe se ikony budou tvoźit ve 256ti barvįch.

@{u}NOTOOLTYPES/S@{uu}
Do ikony se nezapķīķ tooltypy s informacemi o obrįzku. Je-li tento argument zadįn, DT2NI zkopķruje tooltypy existujķcķ ikony.

@{u}SECONDIMAGE/S@{uu}
Vytvoźķ se i druhż (inverznķ) obrįzek, kterż se poułije po kliknutķ na ikonu.

@{u}NICONCOLORS/S@{uu}
Pro ikonu se poułije jen 16 barev. Tento argument potlaēķ argument 'GREY'

@{u}NOBACKFILL/S@{uu}
Kolem ikony se nevytvoźķ ēernż rįmeēek. Ikona pak nemusķ bżt ētvercového tvaru.
@endnode


